{{! Inline JobApplication status line-chart (CC-106 #3). Renders only when the
    rich projection carries at least one parseable timeline event — an absent /
    empty / all-malformed timeline drops the whole block (no empty axis frame),
    mirroring the rich-card pills' null-safe drop. The svg redraws via the
    on-render modifier whenever @timeline changes. Tailwind/HyperUI utilities
    only, every color paired with a dark: sibling; the chart sits inside the
    post card's bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 surface. }}
{{#if this.points.length}}
  <div
    data-test-ja-timeline
    class="mt-3 border-t border-gray-200 pt-3 dark:border-gray-700"
  >
    <h4
      class="mb-1 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
    >
      Application status
    </h4>
    <svg
      class="ja-timeline block h-auto w-full"
      role="img"
      aria-label="Application status over time"
      {{on-render this.draw @timeline}}
    ></svg>
  </div>
{{/if}}